#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:2
msgid "COMPILE_OPTIONS"
msgstr "COMPILE_OPTIONS"

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:6
msgid "List of additional options to pass to the compiler."
msgstr "要傳遞給編譯器的額外選項清單。"

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:8
msgid ""
"This property holds a :ref:`semicolon-separated list <CMake Language Lists>` "
"of options and will be added to the list of compile flags when the sources "
"of this file set are built.  The options will be added after target-wide "
"options and source level ones."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:13
msgid ""
"Contents of ``COMPILE_OPTIONS`` may use \"generator expressions\" with the "
"syntax ``$<...>``.  See the :manual:`cmake-generator-expressions(7)` manual "
"for available expressions.  However, :generator:`Xcode` does not support per-"
"config per-source settings, so expressions that depend on the build "
"configuration are not allowed with that generator."
msgstr ""
"``COMPILE_OPTIONS`` 的內容可以使用語法 ``$<...>`` 的「生成器表達式」。請參"
"閱 :manual:`cmake-generator-expressions(7)` 手冊以了解可用的表達式。但是，:"
"generator:`Xcode` 不支援依組態和依來源的設定，因此不允許在該生成器中使用依賴"
"於建置組態的表達式。"

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:20
msgid "Usage example:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:22
msgid ""
"set_property(FILE_SET SOURCES TARGET foo PROPERTY\n"
"  COMPILE_OPTIONS \"-Wno-unused-parameter;-Wno-missing-field-initializer\")"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:27
msgid "Related properties:"
msgstr "相關屬性："

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:29
msgid ""
"Use :prop_fs:`COMPILE_DEFINITIONS` to pass additional preprocessor "
"definitions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:30
msgid ""
"Use :prop_fs:`INCLUDE_DIRECTORIES` to pass additional include directories."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_fs/COMPILE_OPTIONS.rst:32
msgid "Related commands:"
msgstr "相關命令："

